Langchain Introuduction:

What is langchain?
-  Lngchain is a frmework that helps developers build generative ai Applications using LLM model.
-  It provides a structured way to incorporate prompts and generate LLMs, making it easier to build intelligent and interactive applications.
-  Used to implement the generative ai apps.

How to Build the ai agent using langchain:?

Step-1 - Install the langchain framework. --> pip install langchain
Step-2 - Install the any AI related -LLMs  to install. (OPENAI/GEMEINI AI)
         For open ai --> pip install openai
         for gemini AI- --> pip install langchain-google-genai. 
         Ex: https://docs.langchain.com/oss/python/integrations/chat/google_generative_ai
         and we need a open api/gemini api key for llm model to run. --> goto respective site and login with any mail id and get the api key.


Setup
To access Google AI models youâ€™ll need to create a Google Account, get a Google AI API key, and install the langchain-google-genai integration package.
Ex: api key - 1234567890ABCDEFGHJKL

Step-2 : Export the key to OS enviroment.
         import os
         os.environ['GEMINI_API_KEY'] = "1234567890ABCDEFGHJKL"



          
